tags: ['camerman', 'neutral drop', 'jeep', '#shorts', '4x4', "abusing mom's car", 'abusing\xa0a\xa0car', 'automovil', 'bad\xa0driving', 'beat on transmission', 'beating on a car', 'best neutral drops', 'blown\xa0motor', 'broken chassis car', 'burnouts', 'cameraman', 'car\xa0abuse', 'ceramic vs glass', 'destroy cars', "don't\xa0do\xa0this\xa0to\xa0your\xa0car", 'donuts', 'drive it like its hot', 'drive\xa0it\xa0like\xa0its\xa0stolen', 'ebrake', 'engine blew', 'every\xa0day\xa0car\xa0abuse', 'hard\xa0driving', 'how to', 'joy\xa0ride\xa0beating\xa0on\xa0a\xa0car', 'junkman', 'luxury\xa0car\xa0burnout', 'old\xa0beater', 'stuntman', "what's it got stuntman"]
channelDescription:
Neutral Drop, arguably the worst thing you can do to your vehicle. We are Neutral Dropping every day with cars and trucks, among other things, like doing donuts and burnouts. Enjoy folks!

When you put your vehicle in neutral gear, rev the RPMs up real high then throw it into drive. Thus making your tires spin. This is normally done on vehicles with automatic transmissions that do not have the power to burnout by fully depressing the gas pedal. Unfortunately, neutral dropping can ruin your transmission or driveshaft.

A burnout is the practice of keeping a vehicle stationary and spinning its wheels, causing the tires to heat up and smoke due to friction.

A donut is a maneuver performed while driving a vehicle. Performing this maneuver entails rotating the rear or front of the vehicle around the opposite set of wheels in a continuous motion, creating a circular skid-mark pattern of rubber on a road and possibly even causing the tires to smoke from friction.

One half of Falcon 9‚Äôs fairing previously supported four Starlink missions, and the other previously supported a Starlink mission and the Transporter-1 mission.

title: Welcome to Unreal Engine 5 Early Access
description:
Unreal Engine 5 will empower game developers and creators across all industries to realize next-generation real-time 3D content and experiences with greater freedom, fidelity, and flexibility than ever before. Today, Unreal Engine 5 enters Early Access - providing you the first chance to get your hands on some innovative new tools for next-generation game development. 

In this video, Chance Ivey, Senior Technical Designer at Epic Games and Galen Davis, Producer/Evangelist for Quixel at Epic Games provide a first look at the game development tools and workflows available in Unreal Engine 5 Early Access before exploring our newest sample project titled "Valley of the Ancient" - a rich and practical example of how the new features in Unreal Engine 5 Early Access can be used.

description:

Wie gut bin ich schon nach der ersten Impfung gesch√ºtzt? Oder: Was sollte ich vor und nach dem Impfen NICHT tun: Schmerzmittel, Sport, Alkohol?

Wichtig zu wissen: Du bist nicht sofort nach dem Impfen gesch√ºtzt. Das Risiko, schwer an Covid zu erkranken, sinkt zwar schon ein paar Wochen nach der Erstimpfung rapide ‚Äì den vollen Impfschutz hast du allerdings erst ein paar Tage nach der zweiten Impfung. Ausnahme: Beim Impfstoff von Johnson&Johnson reicht nur eine Impfung aus, der volle Impfschutz ist hier nach 28 Tagen erreicht. 

Noch ein Hinweis: Wenn wir von mRNA-Impfungen sprechen, meinen wir die Impfstoffe von Biontech oder Moderna. Vektorimpfstoffe sind sowohl AstraZeneca als auch Johnson&Johnson. Da es allerdings von Biontech und AstraZeneca bei uns deutlich mehr Impfstoff als von den anderen beiden gibt, erw√§hnen wir vor allem diese.
